text: Latypovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Maximovksky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 57 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 62 km from Sterlitamak, 10 km from Maximovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Latypovka
